  "system": {
    "description": "<p>You can spend<strong> 1 AP </strong>and <strong>1 MP</strong> to create a 1 Space diameter Arcane Sigil on the ground beneath you that lasts for 1 minute.</p><p>Choose 1 <strong>Spell School</strong> (Abjuration, Enchantment, Necromancy, etc.) or 1 <strong>Spell Tag</strong> (Fire, Cold, Teleportation, etc.) when you create the Arcane Sigil. The Arcane Sigil radiates magic of the chosen type.</p><p><strong>Using a Sigil:</strong> While a creature is within the area of your Arcane Sigil, it has ADV on <strong>Spell Checks </strong>to cast or produce the effects of Spells with the chosen Spell School or Spell Tag.</p><p><strong>Moving a Sigil:</strong> You can spend <strong>1 AP</strong> to teleport one of your Sigils within 10 spaces to your current space, but multiple Sigils can’t coexist in the same Space.</p>",
